Coming back to the static/dynamic typing conversation of a few days ago (ephemerality thy name is Slack), what do yinz think of:
```static void m(String s) {
	System.out.println("String");
}

static void m(Object o) {
	System.out.println("String");
}

public static void main(String[] args) {
	String s = "s";
	Object o = s;
	m(s); // prints "String"
	m(o); // prints "Object
}```

